r />\nIG 到個文法網上課程 前個年全靠佢我先升到分<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/22/152531_46fbb5e15ead4282eedead1348721f2d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F22%2F152531_46fbb5e15ead4282eedead1348721f2d.jpg&h=aa177ba7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n利申：免費打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed91dca70c098c4af2b65fe5704e4abd2c081a5e","tid":814863,"uid":52062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d7c56096eb1fcb30f0308751c0a9f683dc0dd640","tid":814863,"uid":985,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T14:30:46.000Z","msg":"grammar in use.<br />\n呢排都想滴起心肝學翻好小小d英文，開始睇下美劇(英文字幕)，睇下national geographic，youtube english channel。<br />\n有無咩course推薦？可以用可持續進修基金。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T07:45:09.000Z","msg":"建議初學者唔好諗住聽英文歌睇美劇學文法<br />\n只會越來越亂<br />\nYoutube片都應該由拍黎for學英文既片睇起,<br />\n起初配中文字幕, 後尾慢慢關字幕睇<br />\n<br />\n去到後期有少少底, 先開始睇劇同聽歌會好d,  但都係for學accent同vocab, slang之類"},{"pid":"62bd86d082c411e1b48420fd0d36b0eccbbf7b31","tid":814863,"uid":80481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68f2360c1c387497882e2ff280bb36c2e5d5ee92","tid":814863,"uid":14341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T15:55:27.000Z","msg":"有無啲主要focus 係sentence structure 既書介紹？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋成日用唔到英文既方法諗野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T09:53:50.000Z","msg":"其實真係唔使用咩英文既方法諗野，因為只要你母語唔係英文就一定會有由母語翻譯做英文既過程，只不過啲英文勁人既呢個過程快到佢自己都察覺唔到。如果有人話佢母語係中文而佢做到用英文諗野，一定係呃你。"},{"pid":"b795d596e16df111a97a0c177a881923a6e55515","tid":814863,"uid":14341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62bd86d082c411e1b48420fd0d36b0eccbbf7b31","tid":814863,"uid":80481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68f2360c1c387497882e2ff280bb36c2e5d5ee92","tid":814863,"uid":14341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"